          "page": 30,
          "content": "Po-Lin Chen1, Chih-Hao Chen2, Sung-Chun Tang2, Li-Ming Lien3, Ku-Chou Chang4, Jiunn-Tay Lee5, Chung-Hsiang Liu6, Yu-Wei Chen7, Lung Chan8, Ya-Ju Lin9, Pi-Shan Sung10, Sheng-Yang Hsieh11, Chih-Ping Chung12, Jiann-Shing Jeng2, Taiwan Stroke Society Guideline Consensus Group 1Stroke Center, Department of Neurology, Neurological Institute, Taichung Veterans General Hospital, Taichung, Taiwan. 2Department of Neurology, National Taiwan University Hospital, Taipei, Taiwan. 3Department of Neurology, Shi…",
