          "content": "to mandate COVID-19 acute stroke protocols, including methods and timing of stroke code initiation, brain CT examination under adequate protection, and arrangement of hospital beds. The protocol should specifically emphasize patient triage, including a separation of patients with a low risk from those with a high risk of COVID-19 during ER triage assessment.",
