          "content": "Chih-Hao Chen1, Chi-Hung Liu2, Pi-Shan Sung3, Cheng-Yang Hsieh4, on behalf of Young Stroke Neurologist Development Committee of Taiwan Stroke Society, approved by the secretariat, executive directors and chairman of the Taiwan Stroke Society 1Department of Neurology, National Taiwan University Hospital, Taipei, Taiwan. 2Department of Neurology, Chang Gung Memorial Hospital, Taoyuan, Taiwan. 3Department of Neurology, National Cheng Kung University Hospital, Tainan, Taiwan. 4Department of Neurolog…",
