          "id": "g006_s09",
          "level": 1,
          "heading": "3. We recommend all health care institutions to",
          "page": 4,
          "content": "implement telemedicine facilities on acute stroke code patients and patients who require neurological consultations, to allow neurologists to remotely evaluate patients and reduce unnecessary exposure. We made the above recommendations with the understanding that Taiwan has a majority of confirmed cases being from abroad and has only sporadic community transmission. However, with the everchanging nature of the pandemic, should large-scale community infections occur, the above recommendations wil…",
          "refs": [],
          "subsections": []
        }
