              "level": 2,
              "heading": "Keywords: acute minor ischemic stroke, consensus statement, dual antiplatelet therapy, transient ischemic",
              "page": 1,
              "content": "attack. *, Corresponding author: Dr. Jiunn-Tay Lee, Department of Neurology, Tri-Service General Hospital, Taipei, Taiwan. Dr. Chip-Jin Ng, Department of Emergency Medicine, Chang Gung Memorial Hospital, Taoyuan, Taiwan. E-mail: jiunntay@gmail.com ; ngowl@ms3.hinet.net DOI: 10.6318/FJS.202206_4(2).0002",
