          "page": 1,
          "content": "Dual Antiplatelet Therapy in the Management of Acute Minor Ischemic Stroke and High-Risk Transient Ischemic Attack: An Expert Consensus Statement from Taiwan Stroke Society and Taiwan Society of Emergency Medicine 62",
          "refs": [],
